Titolo: Harley-Davidson: Race Across America

Anno: 1999

Descrizione: Harley-Davidson: Race Across America is a racing game developed by Canopy Games and G2M Games, and published by WizardWorks in 1999. The game centers on racing Harley-Davidson motorcycles across different locales in the United States, with the ultimate goal being to reach the Sturgis Motorcycle Rally.
A version of the game was developed by Running Dog and also released for the Game Boy Color in 2000. Race Across America was later followed by Harley-Davidson: Wheels of Freedom, released in 2000.